name: Klava Grin
description: I’m into just about anything. I love Basket Ball, reading, working out, running, swimming, love to stay home and watch movies, love to cook (maybe you’ll let me cook for you one day), love to listen two a wide range of music: (definitely not into rap unless it’s Christian Rap), but other than that I love Mexican, Christian, Classical, Opera, Techno, Jazz, etc., and sometimes to kill time or wind down I’ll play video games .
